reviewText: If you are a fan of unintentional comedy, buy this immediately.  You will not be disappointed.

Where is Leo?
I was so excited to order this video, I thought nothing of paying the $35 shipping cost. Imagine my excitment when Leo dropped through my letter box, I set the scene to watch it; I was suitably dressed for a tour of Leo's favourite hotspots. Within  moments I was utterly crushed! Leo isn't even in it! I don't know how much research you did on this, I know more about Leo than you so called experts. WHAT I WOULD LIKE TO KNOW IS IF LEONARDO WAS HARMED IN THE MAKING OF THIS MOCKUMENTARY!
I wan't a full REFUND, and I feel I should be compensated for this atrocity, a night out with Leo will suffice.
You have left me anguished and alone, my life shall never be the same

Yours,
Leonara DiCappuchino
